Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看電視的時候請保持室內光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好保持距離觀看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遵守的人...斬!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全第一  為了避免受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們做預備操吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先舒展筋骨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸展  伸展  伸展伸展伸~展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把雙手張開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做擴胸運動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸氣  吸氣  吸氣吸氣吸~氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來大家都很努力的在做著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要加油才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是她回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(420,380)}『歸來的新面孔』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你了,可惠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,他就是太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做可惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說我不在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏發生了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰做的爛玩具暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把房子搞壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還害防禦系統失靈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果讓慈善王家侵入領空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來還被人用槍指著頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在說你,依良!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把警備責任交給你來負責的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  沒關係啦  大家都沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我出發之前比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女傭隊的緊張感好像降低了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是受了你的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會容許這樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,瑪麗耶爾...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍可惠小姐是花右京家警備部門的最高負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,我最怕她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到歐洲出差去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個非常有責任感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有她在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗耶爾,有聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的當家在那裏做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人說想要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能允許大郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就讓他幫忙做房子的修復工作...啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你馬上放下工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話應該我來講才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為當家的為什麼要親自動手做?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是幫忙綁鋼架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一受傷了...那怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣說,可是我沒受傷過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都是這樣工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家的女傭隊除了一部份人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是特殊菁英隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你來操心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我無法打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦,還差一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是刺客的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人現在已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,你完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花右京家的敵人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候會出現真正的刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有義務保護身為當家的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算是在家裏打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為警備人員的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是無法許可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照你的話去做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請你再通融一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了這麼多你還是不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要做工賺錢呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有理由必須工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果不是自己賺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶點已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惠也要不要喝一杯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,....數日後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...去買東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...謝謝你,但是我想自己一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼瑪麗耶爾,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是考驗我嗎?太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天真的不行,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心,瑪麗耶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他到底想買什麼東西呢?)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(從剛才就一直在逛首飾店)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(真是沒用的男人)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你躲在那裏沒用的,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(怎麼可能...我已經保持距離了)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道我會跟來?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是猜測而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你一定會跟來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(這個傢伙...)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你找我做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想借助你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以幫我選?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝了  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不知道女孩子喜歡些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是根據我的興趣選的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不敢保證會有什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要送給女傭們的禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她們很照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也很努力的幫忙修理房子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才硬要打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,不用自己賺來的錢買的話不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來,這是給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你是想要買送給瑪麗耶爾的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼...怎麼突然這樣講?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是猜測而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道你的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你那麼喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去抱她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要亂講
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,瑪麗耶爾不管是什麼要求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她都會答應的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都看太郎大人想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(太郎大人)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(瑪麗耶爾)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...你好像有點搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的感情不是這樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是我太愚昧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們做個朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這傢伙甩掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們最好不要打擾我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!我不是在和你講話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架的話就來試試啊...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要跳出來?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你不用擔心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家一定在擔心我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站得起來嗎,太郎大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來,大家排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要送給我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們感謝之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼東西呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶...這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(貍貓)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人真沒品味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的人的健康都多虧有她負責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6話『快樂的校園生活 任務2』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回也要好好的聽主人差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫療部門的責任者,森雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有女傭隊的健康
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是由她管理的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家能夠安心的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然治療方式有點誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花右京女傭隊
